  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, FastBERT incorporates a dynamic layer adjustment mechanism to reduce computational complexity.",
    "This means that the model can adaptively modify the number of execution layers for each sample.",
    "For simpler samples, FastBERT utilizes fewer layers for prediction, while employing deeper layers for more intricate samples.",
    "Moreover, FastBERT incorporates a distinctive self-distillation processing mechanism that enables faster and more accurate results while minimizing changes to the model structure.",
    "The inferential process of FastBERT is illustrated in Figure 9."
  ]
